top_stories.title: Build an intelligent photo search using Amazon Rekognition, Amazon Neptune, and Amazon Bedrock
top_stories.description: In this post, we show you how to build a comprehensive photo search system using the AWS Cloud Development Kit (AWS CDK) that integrates Amazon Rekognition for face and object detection, Amazon Neptune for relationship mapping, and Amazon Bedrock for AI-powered captioning.
top_stories.author: Kara Yang

top_stories.title: Recraft V4: image generation with design taste
top_stories.description: Recraft V4 generates art-directed images — and actual editable SVGs — with strong composition, accurate text rendering, and what the Recraft team calls "design taste." Four models are available on Replicate now.
